CatDescriptText: The issue of Time Magazine in the lower right corner is from Friday, November 26, 1965, and the cover story features Cleveland Browns football player Jim Brown.
TitMainTitle: Judge Henry Smith handing framed certificate inscribed "Certificate of Life Membership... Alpha Phi Alpha Auxiliary... National Association for the Advancement of Colored People..." to woman, surrounded by three other women, in interior with landscape painting, and magazines including "Time" and "Better Homes and Gardens"
